                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> et Iunoni Reg<lb break="no" n="2"/>in<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ives</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omani</ex></expan> et Lai consis<lb break="no" n="2"/>tentes vico Secun<lb break="no" n="3"/>dini posuerunt <lb n="4"/>pro salute <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ant</abbr><ex>oni</ex></expan> Gordi<lb break="no" n="6"/>anus <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/>cura agentibus <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>magg</abbr><ex>istris</ex></expan> Bonoso B<lb break="no" n="9"/>onunis et Iusto <lb n="10"/>Iustini Pio et <lb n="11"/>Proculo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundjahr 1923-1925. Z. 1 u. 2 befinden sich auf der corona. Unterhalb der letzten Zeile zwei große hederae. (B): AE 1927: Z. 9: argentibus; Lambrino: Z. 7: Antonius.</p>
